<p><strong>Q: What is the main purpose of this edition of Spaceflight Dynamics by Wiesel?</strong>
A: The 3rd edition of Spaceflight Dynamics by Wiesel provides a comprehensive and updated text on the fundamental principles of spaceflight, covering topics from astrodynamics to spacecraft design and control.</p>
